text:
Has anyone ever had issues with an icon field in a nested forloop?  This just says cannot resolve property

```{% for item in module.card_group %} 
---
  {% for item2 in item.card_list_group %}
    &lt;div class="CardListItem gap8 d_flex {% if loop.index &gt; 1 %} pt60 {% endif %}"&gt;
      &lt;div class="CardListSvg"&gt;                    
        {% icon
          name="{{ item2.icon.name }}"
          style="{{ item2.icon.type }}"
          unicode="{{ item2.icon.unicode }}"
          icon_set="{{ item2.icon.icon_set }}"
        %}
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  {% endfor %}
---
{% endfor %}```

Same happens when I try a fresh new module just to test.

```{% for item in module.group_1 %}
	{% for item2 in item.group_2 %}
		{% icon
			name="{{ item2.icon_field.name }}"
			style="{{ item2.icon_field.type }}"
			unicode="{{ item2.icon_field.unicode }}"
			icon_set="{{ item2.icon_field.icon_set }}"
		%}
	{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}```
